# Python Testing

- Framework: pytest with strict markers (`--strict-markers`)
- Markers: `@pytest.mark.unit`, `@pytest.mark.integration`, `@pytest.mark.e2e`
- E2E tests use Playwright and require the dev server running on `localhost:3000`
- Integration tests hit the live PokéAPI — no mocks
- Unit tests validate Python mirror modules in `app/engine.py` and `app/utils.py`
- Shared fixtures live in `tests/conftest.py`
- Coverage target: 80% minimum (`fail_under = 80` in `pyproject.toml`)
- Run tests: `pytest tests/unit/ -v`, `pytest tests/integration/ -v`, `pytest tests/e2e/ -v`
